    <h1>Tic-Tac-Toe</h1>
    <h3>How To Play</h3>
    <p>Player 1: Create a new game by entering the username</p>
    <p>Player 2: Enter another username and the room ID that is displayed on first window.</p>
    <p>Click on the join game button</p>
    <hr>
    <p>
        <h3>Create a new Game</h3>
        <form method="POST" action="/new_game_submit">
            <input type="submit" name="btnNewGame" class="button_sm" value="New Game">
        </form>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p>
        <h3>Join an existing game</h3>
        <form method="POST" action="/join_game_submit">
            <input type="text" name="room" id="room" placeholder="Game ID" required>
